实现一个二分查找算法来在一个有序数组中找到特定元素的代码如下：

```C++
int binarySearch(const int* array, int length, int target) {
    if (length < 1) {
        return -1;
    }
    int low = 0, high = length - 1;
    while (low <= high) {
        int mid = low + (high - low) / 2;
        if (array[mid] == target) {
            return mid;
        } else if (array[mid] < target) {
            low = mid + 1;
        } else {
            high = mid - 1;
        }
    }
    return -1;
}
```

